### REST API Implementation


### DELETE PRODUCT 

REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=tindapress/v1/globals/delete
- Params: key=id (value=id)

RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Plugin Missing!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Verification issues!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'This product does not exists.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'This product is already inactive.' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'An error occured while submitting data to the server.' data: null

IF SUCCESS:
```
    {
        "status": "success",
        "message": "Data has been deleted successfully."
    }
```


#### LIST PRODUCTS BY STORE ID 

REQUEST:
- Method: POST
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=snky (value=session key), key=wpid (value=wordpress id), key=stid (value= Store id)

RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Plugin Missing!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Request Unknown!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator.  Request unknown missing parameters!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Please contact your administrator. ID not in valid format!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'Store id not found.' data: null

IF SUCCESS:
```
    
```

#### INSERT PRODUCT => tindapress/v1/product/insert

REQUEST:
- Method: GET
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=wpid (value=User ID), key=session key (value=User snky), key=stid (value = Store id), key=title (value = title of product ), key = preview (value = preview of product ), key=short_info (value = short info of product ), key= long_info (value = long info of product ), key=sku (value = stock keeping unit ), key= price (value = price ), key= weight (value = weight ), key= dimension (value = dimension )
RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Plugin Missing!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator.  Verification Issues!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator.  Request unknown!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. ID is not in valid format!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'This store does not exists..' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'An error occured while submitting data to database.' data: null

IF SUCCESS:
```
    {
        "status": "success",
        "message": "Data has been added successfully!"
    }
```


#### SELECT PRODUCT BY CATEGORY ID => tindapress/v1/product/category/select

REQUEST:
- Method: GET
- Header: key=Content-Type, value=application/x-www-form-urlencoded
- Params: key=snky (value=session key), key=wpid (value=wordpress id), key = pid (Value = product id)
RESPONSE:
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Plugin Missing!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. Request Unknown!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator.  Request unknown missing parameters!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Please contact your administrator. ID not in valid format!' data: null
- code: 'unknown' message: 'Required fields cannot be empty!' data: null
- code: 'failed' message: 'No product found.' data: null

IF SUCCESS:
```

